  persona5_calculator
  https://github.com/chinhodado/persona5_calculator
  Licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0

  persona5_calculator is itself derived from persona-fusion-calculator
  by Anthony Lieuallen (https://github.com/arantius/persona-fusion-calculator),
  whose copyright is retained in the LICENSE file of both projects.
  The Persona 5-specific data, fusion tables, skill data, and ongoing
