  Copyright 2013, Anthony Lieuallen

The following source files in this repository are derived from persona5_calculator:

  src/data/PersonaDataRoyal.ts   (adapted from data/PersonaDataRoyal.ts)
  src/data/SkillDataRoyal.ts     (adapted from data/SkillDataRoyal.ts)
  src/data/ItemDataRoyal.ts      (adapted from data/ItemDataRoyal.ts)
  src/data/Data5Royal.ts         (adapted from data/Data5Royal.ts)
  src/engine/FusionCalculator.ts (adapted from src/FusionCalculator.ts)

Adaptations made: converted from AngularJS/global-variable pattern to ES modules
(TypeScript named exports); added getRecipesDeep() for recursive tree building.
All fusion logic, arcana tables, persona stats, skill data, and special/rare combo
lists originate from the above upstream projects.

The companion/ subdirectory contains a Windows save reader that incorporates
work from two additional Apache 2.0 projects:

  fiber-saveutil
  Copyright (c) zarroboogs
  https://github.com/zarroboogs/fiber-saveutil
  The AES-256-CBC decryption logic in companion/Decryption.cs is ported from
  fiber-saveutil's save.py module.

  KingdomSaveEditor
  Copyright (c) Xeeynamo
  https://github.com/Xeeynamo/KingdomSaveEditor
  The compendium offsets (0x41D8, 464 × 48-byte entries) and the
  persona ID → name lookup table (companion/Resources/persona-ids.txt,
  copied from KHSave.LibPersona5/Resources/Persona5/Royal_Demon.txt)
  are from KHSave.LibPersona5.

